description: Demolition of the existing buildings and the construction of a new residential-led mixed use development comprising 769 residential units, 1,125 sq. m (GIA) of mixed use floorspace (Use Classes A1-A5, B1a and D1), new public and communal open space and basement car parking within four buildings ranging from 9-17 storeys in height.
